condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Annual Work Plan and Budget (Schedule 2, Section IB, Paragraph 3) | Description :The Borrower shall: (a) prepareand furnish to the Bank by April 30 in each year - beginning in the calendar year 2019 - a proposed Project's consolidated annualwork plan and budget for the following Fiscal Year; (b) taking into account the Bank's comments, finalize the plan and furnish itto Bank for its approval not later than June 30 in each year - beginning in the calendar year 2019; (c) adopt the plan as shallhave been approved by the Bank (Annual Work Plan and Budget) and proceed thereafter to implement the Annual Work Plan and Budget,in a manner satisfactory to the Bank. The Borrower shall not amend, suspend, abrogate or waiver said Annual Work Plan and Budget orany of its provisions without the prior written agreement of the Bank. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Mid Term Review (Schedule 2, Section II, Paragraph 2) | Description :No later than June 30, 2020, the Borrowershall, in conjunction with the Bank, carry out a mid-term review of the Project, covering the progress achieved in theimplementation of the Project. | Due Date :30-Jun-2020. The mid-term review's due date is postponed to 30 June 2021.
